Usage: setBumpPlacementStatus [-help] {PLACED FIXED COVER}
                              {-bumpName <string> | -selected}

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
{PLACED FIXED COVER}             # Bump Placement Status (enum, required)
-bumpName <string>               # Bump Name (string, required)
-selected                        # Set placement status on selected bumps
                                 # (bool, required)